trans-unit.source: Represents an unsigned rights managed <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref> or an unsigned <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref> template.
trans-unit.target: 表示无符号的权限管理<xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref>或无符号<xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref>模板。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> defines security data about rights, users, and other security-related information.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>定义有关权限、 用户和其他与安全相关的信息的安全数据。</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>

trans-unit.source: The license defines how a specific user on a specific computer can use specified rights-managed content.
trans-unit.target: 该许可证定义特定的计算机上的特定用户可以如何使用指定的权限管理的内容。

trans-unit.source: The publishing process begins with the document author, who defines rights information in an UnsignedPublishLicense.
trans-unit.target: 发布过程首先文档作者，UnsignedPublishLicense 中定义权限信息。

trans-unit.source: Next, the authoring application calls the UnsignedPublishLicense.<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UnsignedPublishLicense.Sign%2A> method to create a signed <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.
trans-unit.target: 接下来，创作应用程序调用 UnsignedPublishLicense。<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UnsignedPublishLicense.Sign%2A>方法来创建签名的<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UnsignedPublishLicense.Sign%2A>

trans-unit.source: The signed <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> can then be provided to the end-user client application which can call <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense.AcquireUseLicense%2A> to request an end-user <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>然后可以提供给最终用户客户端应用程序，其可以调用<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense.AcquireUseLicense%2A>来请求最终用户<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense></xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense.AcquireUseLicense%2A></xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>签名

trans-unit.source: The returned <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> then allows the client application to exercise the rights that are granted to the user.
trans-unit.target: 返回<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>然后允许客户端应用程序测试都将授予用户的权限。</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>

trans-unit.source: The document author can use the UnsignedPublishLicense class either to create a signed <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>, or to build and serialize a <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> template.
trans-unit.target: 文档作者可以使用 UnsignedPublishLicense 类或者创建一个已签名<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>，或以生成并序列化<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>模板。</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>

trans-unit.source: As with other <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement> types, UnsignedPublishLicense is only usable in full trust applications.
trans-unit.target: 与其他<xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>类型，UnsignedPublishLicense 是仅可用于完全信任应用程序。</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>
